snippet.title: The Dream of Shadowlands Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the first trailer for my upcoming game, "The Dream of Shadowlands"! This trailer uses voice recordings that are going to be replaced eventually to be a bit higher quality (Specifically the ones spoken by Rina and Jyl), but I had to work with what I had at the time of editing this trailer together.

Itch.io: https://kitty-cay.itch.io/the-dream-of-shadowlands
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1457480/The_Dream_of_Shadowlands/
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/czavaleta
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/cata.zava.game.dev/
